{"type": "article", "id": 29643, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-07-14T23:02:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 30209, "name": "Studio Nienke Hoogvliet"}, {"id": 30210, "name": "Studio Brichet Ziegler"}, {"id": 30211, "name": "Tait Design"}, {"id": 30212, "name": "Nik and Carole"}, {"id": 30213, "name": "Kwanjun Ryu"}, {"id": 30214, "name": "Saif Faisal"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160714181005Rb9DtjAuvK3aqkl6.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h3>Branch fan by Kwanjun Ryu</h3>\n<p>韩国设计师 Kwanjun Ryu 最近将可调节的折臂同小风扇结合，设计一款名为 Branch 的桌上小风扇。它的造型很容易使人联想到动画工作室皮克斯的那个“看板灯” Luxo，看上去简洁又迷你。归功于折臂和能够随意旋转的风扇头，你可以随心所欲地控制风扇把凉爽的风送往需要的地方，有着极高的灵活度。美中不足的是它目前还处于原型阶段，尚未投入生产。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233819aq5yxMJub8IkpXKv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.427619\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233819CNDAhkRQYKqv7cUw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.544762\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607142338199ZO4n6CAtTvEWGLd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.554286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607142338209LWHd3Jh1mTUDAVS.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.586667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233820Ze3mpG8Fq9Xz5tV6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233820xwPVjMzsAJaU2fOB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h3>Poise lamp by Saif Faisal</h3>\n<p>还记得我们曾经介绍过的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/29071.html\">平衡灯</a>吗？今天介绍的 Poise 同样是一款鼓励你动手操作的灯具，由来自印度的 <a href=\"http://www.saif-faisal.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Saif Faisal</a> 设计。纤细的灯柱和灯罩均由一整块核桃木片打造，通过一个圆形的金属扣相连，可以自由地沿着灯柱镂空的部分上下移动。金属扣有黄铜和黑色铝合金两种可选，并且和底座材质保持一致。Faisal 为 Poise 设计了台灯和落地灯两种款式，你可以通过 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SAIFFAISAL.designworkshop\" rel=\"nofollow\">Facebook</a> 主页与他联系进行订购。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233750rPGht8qDOUymu9lH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016071423375204oAyzCDYuIFa91n.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233750PA3aGNwOuther4HC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.935897\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233751TnDlFtLaMSNJBQ9u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233751mxkNb0oQWvwy6gdE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233751YT5UXrNZy9R82JxV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h3>SEA ME Collection by Studio Nienke Hoogvliet</h3>\n<p>提到海草，你能想象到它也可以被制成柔软的纱线、甚至是生物塑料吗？<a href=\"http://www.nienkehoogvliet.nl/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Studio Nienke Hoogvliet</a> 就花了两年时间对海草进行研究，希望可以将这种特殊的材料运用到设计当中，最后的成品就是由一把椅子和一个小桌组成的 <a href=\"http://www.nienkehoogvliet.nl/portfolio/sea-me-collection/\" rel=\"nofollow\">SEA ME</a> 家具系列。为了做到零浪费，设计师们不仅用染色和晒干过程中遗留下的染料为桌子上色，还将一些剩余的废弃物制成了生物塑料碗，与桌子配套摆放。虽然 SEA ME 的两款家具的外观无法和海草联系在一起，仔细端详之后依然会发现斑驳的纤维纹路，仿佛可以闻到大海的气息。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233724iqS81GYyIRa2ehsb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233724oilWfZMm9kLzCynQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233724RFUKCuMDad6PW2pL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233724HsEKJ2xT7Oo6ImeQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233724w7GHQo9FTeUajsgP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607142337254Ww1Bb92JDYLkptO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h3>Nello Mirror by Studio Brichet Ziegler</h3>\n<p>镜子作为一款日常家居用品似乎很少与使用者之间进行互动，来自法国的 <a href=\"http://www.studiobrichetziegler.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Studio Brichet Ziegler</a> 希望通过这面名为 Nello 的镜子改变人们对这一物件的刻板印象，让它作为一种室内装饰与光线产生互动。镜面被安装在两面打磨过的金属片外，中间夹有橡皮绳和上漆的木质组件。尽管如此，镜子从侧面看并没有带给人厚重的感觉，可以很自然地融入周围的环境当中。Nello 一共有三个尺寸，直径分别为 30、55 和 80 厘米。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233639FHaLk78KxEnoOu2p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607142336406yjNW5hs9lJn4wKH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233640yWHi6PjzMTBn3emL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607142336412Dvnsj4SigYd5ICR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233641fPj9mTtAeHh5ugwp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h3>Perpetual Calendar by Tait Design Co.</h3>\n<p>如果你依然对纸质挂历感兴趣而且喜欢动手，<a href=\"http://taitdesignco.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tait Design</a> 公司最近推出的 Perpetual Calendar 或许会让你眼前一亮。以旧时的潮汐仪为灵感设计的挂历使用起来非常有趣，只要轻轻转动挂历上三个圆形卡纸，日期就会发生相应的变化。正因为这种简朴的设计，它也不会和其他挂历一样每一年都需要换新，能够一年年重复使用，无论是放在办公室还是家中都很合适。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/shop/design/perpetual-calendar-tait-design-06-24-2016/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 50 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607142335599oQqy0VfTJYeSN8B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233600HxX6wc8pdqrjiL4U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233600B41YoA2qV6fWDS7v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233600RcUqO5QZGyItFz72.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233559jQd82gXBC40wsIac.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233559NmkiKI1ZxUpO4SRH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h3>Mr Stanley’s by Nik and Carole</h3>\n<p>为了在国际市场上吸引更多顾客的关注，Mr Stanley 最近委托 <a href=\"http://nikandcarole.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nik and Carole</a> 为旗下的食品重新设计了一组包装，将英伦风情与各类异域元素融合在了 Stanley 先生的“旅程”当中。装有饼干的铁盒上采用红黑蓝三色印上了双层巴士的插画，复古的画风也帮助强调了品牌悠久的历史。两种糖果则采用了纸盒包装，标志性的大本钟以及电话亭搭配经典的字体与图案，排版简洁明了又不失趣味。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607142335347mxcAWPoL8VukU2X.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.708000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233535E43hRq6UazwKc1AG.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.708000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233535oJ46t3ZOrzaEIs0B.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233536CLG9Kl8yN6UfBqOo.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.708000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233535ChU6a3LFAYSO5TVE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.708000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233536HwiW4XDZVh5OMt9r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607142335367jyMgTFsQuWXp9BH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.708000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}